Proxytunnel - Punching holes through the corporate firewall

Author: Mark Janssen

Explain how proxies work and how proxytunnel takes abuse of them. Show different scenarios where proxytunnel can be useful and present a new method we called "proxy bouncing" to break through any SSL-capable proxy.
